{"tid":2495453,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"仰光軍隊辦公室炸彈襲擊 3軍人重傷","createTime":"2021-04-19T07:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T08:11:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7dc0379b0067eb6deaba8784fc83afb7263cf4da","tid":2495453,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:51:10.000Z","msg":"緬甸反軍政府示威未平息，軍方上周六（17日）在北部城市抹谷（Mogok）鎮壓造成3人死亡，仰光同日發生針對軍方的炸彈襲擊，3名軍方人員重傷。當局加緊打壓新聞自由，媒體《密支那新聞》的3名記者上周先後被捕。<br />\n<br />\n位於曼德勒省的抹谷當日早上有逾千名民眾示威，支持上周五（16日）反對派成立的全國團結政府，示威開始後約45分鐘，警方到場鎮壓，對示威者開槍，最少3人被擊斃，有目擊者指其中兩名死者年約20多歲，分別頭部及腹部中槍。警方又向嘗試撿起屍體的示威者開槍，其後警方上前將屍體運往抹谷公共醫院，另有2人中槍受槍被捕，有片段拍到武裝部隊成員的對話，揚言想殺死示威者。<br />\n<br />\n追訪反政變新聞為主的《密支那新聞》透露，報館的3名記者於上周被軍方拘捕，分別為22歲及23歲男記者哈杰（Ah Je）與克里斯托弗（Christopher），以及22歲女記者瑪苗密密班（Ma Myo Myat Myat Pan），總編輯指他們被囚於軍方的審問中心，憂慮可能被軍方虐待。<br />\n<br />\n此外，上周六仰光軍隊的辦公室在下午約2時遭3枚土製炸彈襲擊，3名軍人受重傷，其中一人情況嚴重。有目擊者指有人從辦公室外投擲炸彈，爆炸後不久就有救護車到場。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on. cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20210418/bkn-20210418160258832-0418_00992_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"756046f7b18fa980cf25aa7c5072924b84f86d6b","tid":2495453,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:52:56.000Z","msg":"好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e398526cb9affd34f19981ca57de2e795be9d2","tid":2495453,"uid":76404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:54:06.000Z","msg":"其實緬甸係咪已經完左？"},{"pid":"641d6099b2faf042012dad5387bfcb12c84f7149","tid":2495453,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37e398526cb9affd34f19981ca57de2e795be9d2","tid":2495453,"uid":76404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:54:06.000Z","msg":"其實緬甸係咪已經完左？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:58:11.000Z","msg":"打緊仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33335a9a8ea534872cdadff6f231b29d793b1dc0","tid":2495453,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:58:54.000Z","msg":"對抗極權政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4230a739851dc769caab10990fd7bb31a8f5d04","tid":2495453,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53b0421c4012c54c1131069d45b6c86ed0e8d26","tid":2495453,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:10:50.000Z","msg":"緬甸班軍人下場一定要不得好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89d35992d07767853529576cbb48dc7c7dd76f1","tid":2495453,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}